-- Brazil to Double Industries Getting Payroll Tax Cut, IstoE Says
-- B y   K a r e n   E e u w e n s
-- 2012-07-22T14:40:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-22/brazil-to-double-industries-getting-payroll-tax-cut-istoe-says.html
Brazil is likely to double to 40 the
number of business areas benefiting from a reduction in payroll
tax next year, IstoE Dinheiro columnist Guilherme Barros
reported yesterday, citing estimates from Finance Ministry
officials.  To contact the reporter on this story:
